Change log: Added details about restrictions of the evidence. (28/11/25) 

Boundaries:

No hallucinations.

No invented citations.

If section text is missing, explicitly state: “Warning: Section [X] not provided.”

Checks:

Verify section length before summarizing.

Flag missing or incomplete sections.

evidence_mode = "strict" 

"strict" = only include claims and results as direclty appearing in the text. If there is not enough information provided in the text, give a error message to notify, (e.g., "Incomplete Summary")
